snippet.title: The Walking Dead: Destinies - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Get your first look at The Walking Dead: Destinies, the new choice-driven action-adventure game where you'll have a chance to rewrite the story of The Walking Dead as you know it, reliving the biggest moments from seasons 1-4 of the TV show. Destinies is in development for PC, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.
